<i>adverb</i>: 쓱 [쓱], 슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍], 슬쩍 [슬쩍], 슬슬 [슬슬], 살짝살짝 [살짝쌀짝], 살짝 [살짝], 살살 [살살], 살며시 [살며시], 몰래 [몰ː래] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>쓱 [쓱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. on the quiet; by stealth; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>소리 없이 슬그머니 내밀거나 들어가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of pushing something out or going into somewhere quietly and stealthily.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stealthily; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>눈에 띄지 않게 슬쩍 사라지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of vanishing stealthily so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quickly</dd><br>
<dd>빨리 지나가는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of passing quickly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. lightly; deftly</dd><br>
<dd>슬쩍 문지르거나 비비는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of rubbing or wiping something lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>5. quickly and quietly</dd><br>
<dd>슬쩍 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a person acting quickly and quietly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and lightly without much effort..</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quietly so that others do not know..</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 잇따라 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession, carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬쩍 [슬쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>Carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬슬 [슬슬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slowly</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 천천히 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly, not hastening.</dd><br>
<dd>8. effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘들이지 않고 쉽게 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing something easily without much effort.</dd><br>
<dt>살짝살짝 [살짝쌀짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly in succession so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly in succession without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Bit by bit and not much.</dd><br>
<dd>4. quietly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly in succession so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt>살짝 [살짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>얽힌 실 등이 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of tangled thread, etc., disentangling easily.</dd><br>
<dt>살며시 [살며시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르도록 조용히 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and carefully so that others do not notice.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly; softly; cautiously</dd><br>
<dd>천천히 가볍고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a slow, light, and careful manner.</dd><br>
<dt>몰래 [몰ː래]</dt><br>
<dd>secretly; in secret; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알지 못하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that others would not notice.</dd><br>
